  "title": "2 year contract Medical Social Worker (Govt Hospital) - #HKH",
  "description": "<p>Responsible for delivery of patients’ service in the work area in a personalized, specialized and cost-effective way in accordance to established hospital policies, procedures and standard of practices.</p><p>Primary Responsibilities and Duties</p><ul><li>To assess for mental health issues, provide case formulation and recommendations for treatment.</li><li>To provide appropriate counseling / psychotherapy for identified inpatients and outpatients.</li><li>To contribute, as part of an inter-disciplinary team, in the overall care plan for the patient.</li><li>As part of an inter-disciplinary team, to facilitate transition to adult-care.</li><li>To develop or improve on workflow for better patient care.</li><li>To initiate and implement new psycho-social programmes</li><li>To assist in the development of materials for teaching and training.</li><li>Provide in-service training for department staff as needed.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Degree in Social Work</li><li>No exp needed - training provided</li><li>Min 2 to 4 years of social worker experience will be an advantage </li></ul><p><strong>Govt Hospital </strong></p><p><strong>Office hours, Mon to Fri</strong></p><p><strong>Interested candidates, please forward your resume to </strong><a href=\"mailto:lifescience@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a><br /></p><p>Consultant: Huang Jingsheng Kevyn (R1333338)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</p>",
